In [12]:
def categorize(loyalty):
    try:
        if loyalty == 1:
            return ''
        elif loyalty == 0:
            return ' '
    except:
        pass
In [13]:
purchases['loyalty_program'] = purchases['loyalty_program'].apply(categorize)
